        <script>
            var english={
                "title":"Giving a Urine Sample",
                "line1":"This is a story about giving a urine sample. A urine sample helps the doctor learn about my body so I can stay healthy. I can tell a trusted adult anytime if I need help or a break.",
                "line2":"A medical assistant will give me a small cup with a lid and some cleaning wipes. The cup is clean and just for me. I will only touch the outside of the cup and the lid.",
                "line3":"I will go into the bathroom. I can close the door for privacy. A parent or caregiver may come with me if I need help.",
                "line4":"First, I will wash my hands with soap and water. Then, I will take the lid off the cup and place it down with the inside facing up.",
                "line5":"I will use the cleaning wipes on my body to help keep germs away from the sample. I will throw each wipe away after using them.",
                "line6":"If I have a penis, I will gently clean the tip of my penis with a wipe using small circular motions. I will use a new wipe each time and clean three times.",
                "line7":"If I have a vulva, I will sit on the toilet and gently separate the folds of skin where my pee comes out. I will use the first wipe to clean the right side, wiping front to back. I will use the second wipe to clean the left side, wiping front to back. I will use the third wipe to clean the middle area, wiping front to back.",
                "line8":"After cleaning, I will start peeing into the toilet. While I am still peeing, I will move the cup under the pee to collect a small amount. I can take my time. It is okay if a little pee misses the cup. A trusted adult can help if needed.",
                "line9":"When there is enough pee in the cup, I can move the cup away and finish peeing in the toilet. Once I am finished, I will put the lid on the cup and close it tightly so nothing can spill out.",
                "line10":"I will wash my hands again with soap and water.",
                "line11":"When I am finished, I may give the cup directly to the medical assistant. In some clinics, I may be asked to leave the cup in the bathroom. The medical assistant will send it to the lab to be tested.",
                "line12":"I did a great job learning how to give a urine sample!",
            }
